### Files
direc  '.'
prefix 'alu'
output '.flt' '.tif' '.ubi' '.par'  

### Images
make_image 1       # generate images if different from 0, default generate
noise 0            # put on noise if different from 0, default no noise
psf 0              # spread of Gaussian point spread function (detector)
